---
title: Tunisian Freekeh Stew with Roasted Spiced Chickpeas and Green Salad
description: Freekeh is an ancient grain that's been toasted and cracked to create it's unique flavour! It's great in salads, but also surprisingly delicious in this Tunisian stew! A unique blend of eight spices gives this dish its smoky and savoury flavour – we guarantee you’ve never tasted anything like it!
